{"tid":1675370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"早排葵涌警署休班警被人斬 破案未？","createTime":"2019-10-25T22:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:39:56.000Z","uid":123774,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2498090af58b0aadb8719ffedaaf89ec5460ba0d","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:22:17.000Z","msg":"高調話情報顯示同反送中有關 捉到人未？<br />\n<br />\n咁多個禮拜以來低調處理<br />\n事實係咪呀sir又欠落賭債 定同黑社會拆唔掂數<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dc9bba614feb404743d044b8e370fcd2490aee","tid":1675370,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:24:43.000Z","msg":"想睇傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7ecfdc947ff48a5c61ab3971dcaec27e631024","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:29:42.000Z","msg":"定係又叫雞唔俾錢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFmu5Mc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFmu5Mc.jpg&h=31b9f292&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3da4b4e40d10054a2fb9fffe70102f0a44d2edf7","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"64dc9bba614feb404743d044b8e370fcd2490aee","tid":1675370,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:24:43.000Z","msg":"想睇傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAVr7ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAVr7ZQ.jpg&h=0e766332&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3a398e3bc36c86e0e71e3171db794c0c396d2a9","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:42:37.000Z","msg":"仲有好多監守自盜案件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警長爛賭欠巨債呃埋情婦錢著草</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTKTN3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTKTN3C.jpg&h=51d99ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160503/55059831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160503%2F55059831&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=91a78b8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160503%2F55059831&h=19c6d954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160503/55059831</a><br />\n<br />\n灣仔警署署理警署警長，昨日擔任報案室值日官期間涉嫌監守自盜偷走107萬保釋金，之後潛逃澳門至今下落不明。警方深入調查其近況，發現他不但有婚外情，更沉淪賭海，欠下財務公司40萬債款，另外欠下巨額「街數」，疑走投無路下鋌而走險。<br />\n<br />\n涉案警長姓張(43歲)，根據入境處出境紀錄，相信他已潛逃澳門。警方翻查內部資料，張從沒呈報欠債紀錄，但本身卻是欠債纍纍，單是財務公司的貸款已達40萬元，銀行貸款及「街數」隨時超過百萬元，相信他為確保可以順利升職，蓄意隱瞞未向警方申報，令警方蒙在鼓裏。<br />\n<br />\n警方偵查下，揭發其私生活也有問題，最近與一名情婦打得火熱，幾個月來已甚少返回油塘油美苑警察宿舍與妻女生活。該情婦向警方承認，張為人爛賭欠下巨債，她也借了不少錢給他，自己亦是受害者之一。警方初步相信，張疑債務壓力爆煲，走投無路下犯案。"},{"pid":"982f63a9e864e84b20e974138f73357aa136cd66","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:45:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>欠賭債監守自盜　督察偷86萬判囚21個月</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2019/51400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-01-2019%2F51400&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=e8a35f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2019/51400</a>"},{"pid":"21a61bc5d73831eeec0946db1d539ade0c609595","tid":1675370,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3da4b4e40d10054a2fb9fffe70102f0a44d2edf7","tid":1675370,"uid":123774,"like":20,"disli